data.description: OPEN SAT 2/24 from 11am-1pm. LAKEFRONT Views w/ huge FL Room, RENOVATED 4BR TURN KEY, 3 Miles to Ocean w/ one of the LOWEST HOA's in PB County!!! Investment/Rental/Family Home. This modern, open beautiful home features 2.5 baths plus floating cabinets, new lighting, new bar height kitchen counter w/ dining space for 6-8, bar & wine cabinet, split BR's w/ master w/dual sinks on 1st level, fresh paint, new laminate flooring 2nd level, built in closet shelves for max storage, 1 car garage w/ extra storage, attic & extra refrigerator, laundry in garage. Enjoy entertaining & relaxing on the huge covered screened in porch with tile flooring. Large private fenced side yard awaits your creativity! Home sits on quiet cul-de-sac in peaceful neighborhood close to shopping & just minutes from 95! Community has super LOW HOA, pool, clubhouse, walking trail & tennis court. Bar, bar stools, 3 large mounted TV's all convey.  All furniture conveys with asking price (or is negotiable). Hurricane panels.  BRAND NEW dishwasher, washer, and GE Profile Range.  BRING ALL REASONABLE OFFERS!
